 be allowed before the pazopanib dosage is adjusted upward.', 'Metabolism', 'Concomitant use of pazopanib with potent CYP450 3A4 inhibitors should generally be avoided.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/151393/', '', 'Futibatinib, Tucatinib, Alpelisib, Lenvatinib, Trametinib, Nintedanib, Vandetanib, Afatinib, Alectinib, Dacomitinib, Tivozanib, Sorafenib', 'Dirithromycin, Lincomycin, Clindamycin', 1767369485);
